    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Patrick County (Va.) Will of Jacob Adams, 1807 December, details how and to whom Adams would like his property distributed to his heirs. Items listed include land, household furniture, livestock, and slaves.
</p>
